ted\nby algorithmically deriving generalized Lax-integrable versions of NLS,\nPT-symmetric NLS, and DNLS equations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Oct 2014 18:57:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-03"}
