ical details of measurement tools and\napparatus as an opportunity for authentic and engaging scientific sense-making.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Oct 2014 15:27:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Jan 2015 15:16:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 Feb 2015 20:27:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-28"}
